      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but it still feels like there's something sneaky going on with the math. like, it feels like a hidden cost that's just eating away at my money every single month. is there any way to see exactly how much of my payment is being taken by interest vs the principal before i actually pay it?",
