      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried using one of those online calculators and it's still hard to grasp. it feels like there are these tiny little things buried in the math that just keep pulling the numbers back up. like, even when i'm following the rules, the total amount just seems to resist going down. do you think there are any other factors or hidden mechanics that could be causing that drag?",
